	<p>
		Hi, I'm Benjamin. I write about the ideas and systems that shape the world — AI, money,
		geopolitics, and technology — explained in plain English, without the jargon.
	</p>

	<p>
		My goal is simple: take complex topics and break them down so clearly that anyone can
		understand them, regardless of their background. If you finish a post and think "I never
		thought about it that way" — that's the win.
	</p>

	<p>
		The posts here cover a wide range. Some explore how AI systems like Claude actually work
		under the hood. Others trace the hidden architecture of global finance — why the dollar
		dominates, how empires rise and fall, what the history of money reveals about the present.
	</p>

	<p>
		Each post comes with a visual companion — interactive diagrams and slide decks that make
		the ideas easier to see, not just read.
	</p>

